            The Catering was founded in Cluj-Napoca by Oana Ujica. Delicious catering for every occasion
            LeGourmet is one of the finest caterers in Cluj-Napoca. We are a family run restaurant that has built an excellent reputation for our delicious food. 
            Tickle your taste buds with flavours from around the world in the city of Cluj-Napoca. Business lunch and large order can now be order the same day delivery. 
            Event catering must be ordered with at least a week’s notice. Get in touch with one of our team members. We understand how important your special event is to you and we have a reputation for on-time delivery, attention to detail and excellent customer service. 
            With over 16 years in this business, we specialise in event catering and business lunch delivery. <a href="#contact">Contact us</a> for further details.
        </p>
        <br>
